### Cascade Risk Analysis
- **If RISK-001 occurs**: Increases probability of RISK-002 by 30%, RISK-003 by 15%
- **If RISK-002 occurs**: Increases probability of RISK-004 by 25%
- **If RISK-003 occurs**: Increases probability of RISK-004 by 40%, RISK-005 by 20%

